A summation operator. sum(f,n+1) is the sum of all f(i), i=0...n.
*)

NatSum = Arith +
consts sum     :: [nat=>nat, nat] => nat
primrec 
  "sum f 0 = 0"
  "sum f (Suc n) = f(n) + sum f n"

end
